cases the <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">writer</ENAMEX> is using a phonetic spelling that reminds
us of the incorrect attempts made by <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">children</ENAMEX>
or the uneducated at spelling these words.

