<NUMEX TYPE="ORDINAL">second</NUMEX> says <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">‚ÄúClimbing</ENAMEX>,‚Äù and the <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG_DESC">leader</ENAMEX> acknowledges,
<ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">‚ÄúAye</ENAMEX>, aye.‚Äù

